{"tid":1179961,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又贏] 中方警告全球金融危機　衝突恐持續30年","createTime":"2019-05-31T13:06:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T14:10:29.000Z","uid":12609,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"70e226f66ce212952c8261179f68b4ac3b55465f","tid":1179961,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T13:06:27.000Z","msg":"外國傳媒報道，中國人民銀行(即中國央行)前行長戴相龍警告，若中美貿易戰再升級，將對全球經濟造成重大災難！<br />\n<br />\n他指出，中美貿易戰的後果不僅僅影響這兩個國家，更會延伸至相關地區，再令全球攬炒。如果中美持續加大反擊力度，或會導致全球經濟下滑，甚為出現全球金融危機。<br />\n<br />\n戴相龍於1995至2002年出任人民銀行行長，有份推動中國市場改革，其言論有一定影響力。<br />\n<br />\n另一位前高官、中國商務部前副部長魏建國亦警告，<strong>美國今次行動的時機錯了，打錯了仗，亦用錯了武器。他強調，今次可能是美國自二次世界大戰後、甚至建國以來，犯下的最大錯誤。</strong>貿易衝突可能會持續30年或以上，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中國會贏</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n美國想輸又要你管<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36b24327c5470498a3fbca6a9caf6fae476cefab","tid":1179961,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T13:30:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"836b05b8dab1aefe2c061181727b50aa36c8a095","tid":1179961,"uid":54264,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T13:33:32.000Z","msg":"侵侵：捱得過我任期當你贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc53319341f365e1bbaa56d631a4aabf9868e8b7","tid":1179961,"uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T13:34:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁1949-1980<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全球零經濟？"},{"pid":"38d134543c7f71eb608a7f3d7f5de0bd7e69f285","tid":1179961,"uid":17510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"836b05b8dab1aefe2c061181727b50aa36c8a095","tid":1179961,"uid":54264,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime